Desc.SourceString: 在沃兰雪原出生，一生都在渴望离开雪原，环游世界。但在14岁那年，自己所在的避难所突发雪崩，父母均死于那场雪崩，唯独被护在身下的自己活了下来。之后被过来传教的神代教所救，在教会生活了4年后，被选为教会的代行者，消除教会内的异端。
Desc.LocalizedString: Born in Warren Snowfield, I had been dreaming of getting away and traveling the world. But when I was 14, an avalanche destroyed our shelter. Both my parents died and only I survived, as they had covered me with their bodies. I was rescued by the church that came to preach. After 4 years of living with them, I was selected as the Executor of the church, responsible for eliminating the heretics among us.
